The paper deals with sensor calibration for spectral estimation, which involves signal processing and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves statistical inference and machine learning techniques, which are covered by cs.SI (Statistical Learning). The paper deals with signal processing and spectral analysis, which are covered by cs.SP (Signal Processing). The paper also involves numerical optimization techniques, which are covered by cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
